Careers
Our commitment to building a stronger energy future is matched by our commitment to our employees who will make it a reality. We equip employees with the resources and support they need to be successful. We encourage teamwork and provide a safe, rewarding work environment.

Available Positions
Benefits
EEO and FMLA Policies
Philosophy
Opportunities for Veterans



Select a business below to view available positions:

































































































Our Goal
Our goal is to bring people and power together to create dynamic, rewarding careers. Begin your career search with us by:



Applying for a currently posted position. Access the job search and application tool to find a job that's the right fit for you. For assistance with completing an application, review our application instructions




Creating a candidate profile. Build an online resume for future positions; submit your preferences for job location, job type and whether you would like to receive correspondence for future job openings.




Having difficulty with the job search and application tool? Get technical support.






What to Expect
You will receive an email confirmation when we've received your application. We will contact you if you are a potential match for the desired position. Since each application received for a posted position is reviewed by our recruiting staff, this process may take up to two weeks.
Employment is contingent upon an acceptable receipt of references, background check, and depending on the business unit requirements, a post-offer, pre-employment physical and/or drug screen. Berkshire Hathaway Energy is an equal opportunity employer.


Applicants With Need for Accommodation
Berkshire Hathaway Energy is an equal opportunity employer that values diversity in the workplace and welcomes applicants who may be differently abled. Applicants in need of accommodation during the application, interview or selection process should contact us, or call our HR Helpline at 800-432-8999. Select option 3, then select option 1 for career inquiries. Please reference the title of the position for which you are applying and the corresponding job number.










